Eike Batista’s OGX Discovers More Oil in Offshore Brazil Campos Basin Well

-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 
2011-06-03T08:06:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/eike-batista-s-ogx-discovers-more-oil-in-offshore-brazil-campos-basin-well.html
OGX Petroleo & Gas Participacoes SA,
the oil company controlled by Brazilian billionaire  Eike Batista , found evidence of oil in an offshore well in the  Campos
Basin .  The discovery was made at well 3OGX42DRJS in the  C-M-592 
block, according to a  posting  on the website of the National
Petroleum Agency. OGX, based in  Rio de Janeiro , hasn’t
determined whether the discovery can be developed commercially.
The company found oil in several nearby wells this year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
